  "text": "Remark 1. In this work, we need to be careful with the term \"patch\" since this one can be employed for both NURBS and global/local coupling algorithm. We emphasize here that the term \"patch\" will only refer to the concept of IGA patch in the following. Thus, the term patch will never refer to the local model (in opposition to [CITATION_1] for example).",
